*Financial statement]]
*FP&amp;A
*Going concern (Fundamental basis of financial statements)
*Managerial risk accounting

==Notes==
==External links==

* SFAF – the French Society of Financial Analysts
* ACIIA – Association of Certified International Investment Analysts
* EFFAS – European Federation of Financial Analysts Societies</text><links>
