===Particular cases===
If formula_24, the transformation is horizontal; when formula_25, it is a dilation, when formula_26, it is a contraction.

If formula_27, the transformation is vertical; when formula_28 it is a dilation, when formula_29, it is a contraction.

If formula_30 or formula_31, the transformation is a squeeze mapping.

